The paper also discusses re-ranking methods and query expansion, which are common techniques in information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of integral images and max-pooling is a technique commonly used in multimedia processing (cs.MM). The paper also discusses feature encoding and vector representation, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG).
